	(8480,27,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','We’re a full service interactive agency in Philadelphia dedicated to helping brands succeed online. We specialize Web Analytics, Search, Development and Design.'),
	(8481,60,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','BrainDo specializes in SEO content strategy, keyword research, technical optimization, link strategy and offers a practical approach to brand discovery online.'),
	(8482,62,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','We specialize in Paid Search & Media bid optimization, copy testing, extensive keyword research, remarketing and landing page strategy.'),
	(8483,110,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','We created a social campaign that out performed all previous posts and engaged a lagging social audience.'),
	(8484,64,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','We’re known for our innovative, in-depth and detailed approach to analytics engineering and Google tag management. Learn more about how BrainDo can impact your business.'),
	(8485,106,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','At the end of the day, we get it done. Check out some of our past work and how we’ve managed to create real results that matter for our clients.'),
	(8648,110,'page_header','Engaging a Social Audience.'),
	(8649,110,'page_sub_header','We created the most engaging and far reaching and engaging campaign our client had ever seen. '),
	(8650,110,'challenge_header','Challenge: '),
	(8651,110,'challenge_content','<p><span class=\"tx\">Our client’s Facebook fans numbered around 20,000 but were primarily composed of current </span><span class=\"tx\">customers and employees. The core audience was moderately active, yet rarely generated </span><span class=\"tx f5\">much social reach among non-fans. The organic reach of posts was about 45% lower than </span><span class=\"tx\">the client’s Facebook fan base.</span></p>'),
	(8652,110,'solution_header','Solution: '),
	(8653,110,'solution_content','<p><span class=\"tx\">We created a social media campaign centered around an interactive quiz that highlighted one of </span><span class=\"tx f910\">the client’s new products in an education, fun way. We designed &amp;</span><span class=\"tx\"> developed the quiz as well </span><span class=\"tx\">as additional education content, social posts and supported the endeavor with social media and </span><span class=\"tx\">paid ads.</span></p>'),
	(8654,110,'results_header','Results:'),
	(8655,110,'results_content','<p class=\"tb f5\"><span class=\"tx\">Through an engaging social campaign we generated a total reach of 700k+ across all social </span><span class=\"tx\">platforms. The top Facebook posts attracted 5x more clicks than any previous post, organic </span><span class=\"tx\">daily reach rose by 117% and Facebook fans increased by 7%. Twitter saw a similar boost to </span><span class=\"tx\">engagement and an increase of 14% new Twitter followers.</span></p><p class=\"tb f5\"> </p><ul><li class=\"tb f5\"><span class=\"tx\">Social Stats: 19 days before the campaign </span><span class=\"tx f910\">–</span><span class=\"tx\"> average daily organic reach of 7,270</span></li><li class=\"tb f5\"><span class=\"tx\">19 days of the campaign </span><span class=\"tx f910\">–</span><span class=\"tx\"> average daily organic reach of 15,797 (117% rise)</span></li><li class=\"tb f5\"><span class=\"tx\">19 days after the campaign </span><span class=\"tx f910\">–</span><span class=\"tx\"> average daily organic reach of 8,664 (return to pre-</span>campaign levels)</li></ul><p class=\"tb f5\"> </p><p class=\"tb f5\"><span class=\"tx\">Paid content increased reach further.  Over 48k people per day were reached using Facebook </span><span class=\"tx\">and Twitter ads. This was the most far reaching and engaging social media campaign our client </span><span class=\"tx\">had ever produced.</span></p>'),
	(8656,110,'case_study_image_url','case-study-social.jpg'),
	(8657,110,'background_image','cs-social.jpg'),
	(8658,110,'background_video',''),
