	(8775,60,'description_header','How do people discover your brand?'),
	(8776,60,'page_description','SEO is no longer about keywords and links alone – it’s about online discovery and perception. We see SEO at the center of many different disciplines. It connects Development, Design, Social, PR, Mobile Apps and CRO to name a few. Our holistic approach to SEO, backed by the team’s extensive experience creating solutions for Fortune 500 clients, ensures we create long lasting results for our clients in Google and beyond.'),
