	(8789,62,'description_header','Our Paid Search team doesn\'t just run Adwords campaigns, we orchestrate them.'),
	(8790,62,'page_description','We’re used to managing multi-million dollar campaigns through Google, Bing, LinkedIn, Twitter & YouTube specializing in bid optimization, copy testing, extensive keyword research, remarketing and landing page strategy. In addition, we use Paid Search and Social Ads to support client marketing initiatives. Whether you’ve been running paid search and want to get more mileage out of it, or are new to Search and need a partner to introduce you to the marketing platform, we can help.'),
