	(8923,104,'page_header','Advanced Analytics'),
	(8924,104,'page_sub_header','Unlocking the Potential of our Client\'s Data'),
	(8925,104,'challenge_header','Challenge:'),
	(8926,104,'challenge_content','<p><span class=\"tx\">Our client needed a unifying structure to implement its analytics across its websites. It often led to </span><span class=\"tx\">confusion during analysis and left gaps of incomplete data. Inconsistent use of custom events, </span><span class=\"tx\">variables and goals made analysis difficult or sometimes impossible.</span></p>'),
	(8927,104,'solution_header','Solution: '),
	(8928,104,'solution_content','<p><span class=\"tx f910\">Apply the BrainDo full host of advanced analytics solutions to assess our client\'s analytics need </span><span class=\"tx\">and roll out the updated tags and analytics measures to improve the </span><span class=\"tx f910\">brand’s overall </span><span class=\"tx\">performance.</span></p>'),
	(8929,104,'results_header','Results:'),
	(8930,104,'results_content','<p><span class=\"tx\">BrainDo implemented an overhaul of their analytics tagging including an optimized user interface </span><span class=\"tx\">that allowed our client to gather more reliable data and access it more intuitively.</span><br /><span class=\"tx\">Analytics Implementation of:</span></p><ul><li><span class=\"tx\">Google Tag Manager, which fires Universal and Classic calls to GA</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Consistency of custom events, variables and goals</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Site Search</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Ecommerce</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Google Web Master Tools</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Form field, form submission, cross domain, download link, telephone link, external link </span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">55 Custom Events</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">10 Custom Variables</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">5 Content Groups</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Custom Channel Groupings</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">10 Goals</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">5 Filters</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Page View customization</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Complete Parity of Universal and Classic</span></li><li><span class=\"tx\">Custom Event-driven 3</span><span class=\"tx\">rd</span><span class=\"tx\"> Party Tag Tracking</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"tx\">Improving the consistency, breadth and depth of our client\'s </span><span class=\"tx f910\">analyti</span><span class=\"tx\">cs allows them to dig deeper, </span><span class=\"tx\">finding better answers more efficiently. Measurement plans were now more straight-forward and </span><span class=\"tx\">product level analysis was more clear and concise.</span></p>'),
	(8931,104,'case_study_image_url','case-study-analytics.jpg'),
	(8932,104,'background_image','cs-analytics.jpg'),
