	(9294,68,'description_header','A CRO analysis is like taking your marketing to the doctor. '),
	(9295,68,'page_description','We seek to diagnosis and remedy problems that are preventing users from having the most optimal experience on your site and ultimately converting. We want to answer the important questions about your website: “What do users do when they reach your site?” “Is your headline off the mark?” “Why aren’t landing pages converting?” “How can we get these pages to convert?” Using a technology cocktail of tools, analytics analysis and tag teaming with creative and development, we run website tests that help us to incrementally improve user interaction and create solutions that work.'),
