	(9319,30,'background_image','service-web-design.jpg'),
	(9320,30,'background_video',''),
	(9321,73,'page_header','Who We Are'),
	(9322,73,'page_sub_header','BrainDo is a full-service, interactive agency with one goal: <strong>Help Our Clients Succeed Online.</strong>'),
	(9323,73,'first_paragraph','BrainDo is a collection of hard working go-getters and experts that come together to create great things for our clients. Our experience lets us cut through the fads and develop the strategy and tactics that truly work to build brand experience and bring measurable results.'),
	(9324,73,'paragraph_header_1','We Get It.'),
	(9325,73,'paragraph_text_1','Our brains aren’t wired faster, we just care more about getting it right. Our team understands how to grow, sustain and reimagine digital brands. We draw on our combined expertise of 50+ years in Digital Marketing having touched on nearly every vertical including: Travel, Automotive, Insurance, Legal, Pharmaceutical, Ecommerce, B2B, Health/Beauty & Fitness and Entertainment.'),
	(9326,73,'paragraph_header_2','We Get It Done.'),
	(9327,73,'paragraph_text_2','The number one reason our clients like us, put simply, “We Get it Done.” Great strategy doesn’t mean squat if you can’t execute – and we execute with precision. We believe clients have the right to great results in a timely fashion and we continue to be the agency known for getting it done and doing it well.'),
	(9328,73,'employee_block_header','Meet the Team'),
	(9329,73,'employee_name','Ben Stuart'),
	(9330,73,'employee_title','Web Analytics & Tag Management'),
	(9331,73,'employee_description','Ben is a die-hard tech enthusiast, building computers in his spare time and then using those computers to develop smart analytics solutions and implement management plans (including detailed documentation flow charts) for our clients.'),
	(9332,73,'employee_image_url','benstuart.jpg'),
	(9333,73,'employee_hover_image_url','benstuart-hover.jpg'),
	(9334,73,'employee_selected_image_url','benstuart-selected.jpg'),
	(9335,73,'employee_name','Bill Paffas'),
	(9336,73,'employee_title','CRO & User Experience'),
	(9337,73,'employee_description','As resident CRO expert, Bill combines his years of digital analytics experience with a keen understanding of user experience. When not testing websites, he often performs multivariate tests on his two dogs: Ralph & Rufus.'),
	(9338,73,'employee_image_url','billpaffas.jpg'),
	(9339,73,'employee_hover_image_url','billpaffas-hover.jpg'),
	(9340,73,'employee_selected_image_url','billpaffas-selected.jpg'),
	(9341,73,'employee_name','Brian Cosgrove'),
	(9342,73,'employee_title','Web Analytics & Digital Strategy'),
	(9343,73,'employee_description','Brian embodies the Zen of Digital Marketing. Brian balances the creative elements of brand development with reasoned, in-depth web analytics engineering, and experienced website development. When Brian’s not empowering our clients, you can probably find him fencing in the park or parkour’ing off a fence.'),
	(9344,73,'employee_image_url','briancosgrove.jpg'),
	(9345,73,'employee_hover_image_url','briancosgrove-hover.jpg'),
	(9346,73,'employee_selected_image_url','briancosgrove-selected.jpg'),
	(9347,73,'employee_name','Brian Schwartz'),
	(9348,73,'employee_title','Brand Development & Design'),
	(9349,73,'employee_description','As Creative in Chief, Brian believes that good design is central to a brand’s identity and creates mind-blowing designs that make us question our very existence. When he’s not shattering our reality, you can find him hanging out in the city with his family, diligently training marathon runners or watching the most boring game of all: golf.'),
	(9350,73,'employee_image_url','brianschwartz.jpg'),
	(9351,73,'employee_hover_image_url','brianschwartz-hover.jpg'),
	(9352,73,'employee_selected_image_url','brianschwartz-selected.jpg'),
	(9353,73,'employee_name','Glenn Steigerwald'),
	(9354,73,'employee_title','Web Development & Design'),
	(9355,73,'employee_description','Glenn uses his in-depth knowledge of all things code to produce custom, responsive websites that are made of, as he claims “just 0’s and 1’s”. When Glenn’s not lying about code, he’s training his horse to win races.'),
	(9356,73,'employee_image_url','glennsteigerwald.jpg'),
	(9357,73,'employee_hover_image_url','glennsteigerwald-hover.jpg'),
	(9358,73,'employee_selected_image_url','glennsteigerwald-selected.jpg'),
	(9359,73,'employee_name','Harris Neifield'),
	(9360,73,'employee_title','Paid Search & Media'),
	(9361,73,'employee_description','Harris takes online advertising and social media to new levels of awesome. He’ll deadlift your heaviest 500 lb. strategic challenges using his years of digital media experience, data analysis skills and CrossFit training.'),
	(9362,73,'employee_image_url','harrisneifield.jpg'),
	(9363,73,'employee_hover_image_url','harrisneifield-hover.jpg'),
	(9364,73,'employee_selected_image_url','harrisneifield-selected.jpg'),
	(9365,73,'employee_name','Harrison Bryant'),
	(9366,73,'employee_title','Web Development & Analytics'),
	(9367,73,'employee_description','Harrison eats HTML for breakfast. He brings hands on experience in JavaScript, JQuery, HTML5 and works with the rest of the development team to troubleshoot issues and build engaging websites.'),
	(9368,73,'employee_image_url','harrisonbryant.jpg'),
	(9369,73,'employee_hover_image_url','harrisonbryant-hover.jpg'),
	(9370,73,'employee_selected_image_url','harrisonbryant-selected.jpg'),
	(9371,73,'employee_name','Jenny Du'),
	(9372,73,'employee_title','Business Development & Digital Strategy'),
	(9373,73,'employee_description','Jenny is all things Digital Strategy. She super-charges client projects with her expertise in brand development, strategic partnerships, and years of experience within the search and media industry. Jenny routinely orchestrates the many moving pieces of our client projects while eating spicy dinner for breakfast and snuggling with her two Dachshund-mix pooches.'),
	(9374,73,'employee_image_url','jennydu.jpg'),
	(9375,73,'employee_hover_image_url','jennydu-hover.jpg'),
	(9376,73,'employee_selected_image_url','jennydu-selected.jpg'),
	(9377,73,'employee_name','Linda Bien'),
	(9378,73,'employee_title','Paid Search & Web Analytics'),
	(9379,73,'employee_description','Master of numbers, data and math, Linda specializes in fine tuning paid campaigns and understanding website data which she translates into actionable, measurable goals.'),
	(9380,73,'employee_image_url','lindabien.jpg'),
	(9381,73,'employee_hover_image_url','lindabien-hover.jpg'),
	(9382,73,'employee_selected_image_url','lindabien-selected.jpg'),
	(9383,73,'employee_name','Mike Anderson'),
	(9384,73,'employee_title','Web Analytics & Documentation'),
	(9385,73,'employee_description','Mike keeps the development and analytics teams running like a well-oiled machine. He also has a keen eye for analytics documentation, Google Tag Management and hockey pucks.'),
	(9386,73,'employee_image_url','mikeanderson.jpg'),
	(9387,73,'employee_hover_image_url','mikeanderson-hover.jpg'),
	(9388,73,'employee_selected_image_url','mikeanderson-selected.jpg'),
	(9389,73,'employee_name','Rodney Morris'),
	(9390,73,'employee_title','Web Analytics & Development'),
	(9391,73,'employee_description','Rodney is the core of the development and analytics team. Wielding the technological building blocks of code and script, he transforms even the most challenging client development ideas into an interactive reality. Rodney would trade his right leg for a good bowl of Pho.'),
	(9392,73,'employee_image_url','rodneymorris.jpg'),
	(9393,73,'employee_hover_image_url','rodneymorris-hover.jpg'),
	(9394,73,'employee_selected_image_url','rodneymorris-selected.jpg'),
	(9395,73,'employee_name','Scott Hinners'),
	(9396,73,'employee_title','Content Strategy & SEO'),
	(9397,73,'employee_description','The resident word-smith on the team, Scott paints with the English language in a way that touches our very soul. He specializes in SEO, content strategy, creating killer tag lines and is a world champ at Rock, Paper, Scissors (for real).'),
